# pipeline.dag -- full three-stage pipeline with DAGMan.
#
# stage 1: N parallel scoring jobs (one per daily CSV).
# stage 2: aggregate + change-point + regression, once, after all scoring finishes.
#
# Run with:
#     condor_submit_dag pipeline.dag
# Monitor with condor_q or condor_watch_q.

JOB score      score.sub
JOB aggregate  aggregate.sub

# After every scoring job returns, HTCondor drops *_agg.csv into the
# submit dir. Collect them into per_file/ so aggregate.sub can ship
# them to its worker as a single directory.
SCRIPT POST score collect_per_file.sh

PARENT score CHILD aggregate
